<%= render 'layouts/scripts' %>
<%= javascript_pack_tag 'signin', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>

<body>
  <%= render partial: "layouts/navbar", locals: {tab: :home} %>

  <div class="welcome container-fluid">
    <%= link_to image_tag("background.jpg", class: "welcomeIMG") %>

    <div class="welomceLabels">
      <h1 class="welcome-label">Welcome to Berkeley's Armenian Student Association</h1>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="firstBody container-fluid">
    <h1 class="whoweare">Who We Are</h1>
    <p class="firstHeader">The UC Berkeley Armenian Student Association cultivates a spirit of appreciation toward
      Armenian history,
      heritage, and culture through active cultural functions, historical and political awareness, as well as, social
      and recreational events. It strives to create an association where Armenians and non-Armenians alike can come
      together, without any outside political affiliations and/or influence.</p>
  </div>


  <div class="welcome2 container-fluid">
    <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide carousel-fade" data-bs-ride="carousel">
      <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="2"></li>
        <li data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="3"></li>
        <li data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="4"></li>
        <li data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="5"></li>
        <li data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="6"></li>
        <li data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="7"></li>
        <li data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="8"></li>
        <li data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="9"></li>
        <li data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="10"></li>
      </ol>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <%= image_tag("ardzagank.jpg", class: "d-block w-100") %>

          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block white-bg">
            <h5 class="carousel-overlay-title">Ardzagank</h5>
            <p class="carousel-overlay-content">Our incredible choir performs in many venues; one of them happened to be
              the Sproul Hall.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= link_to image_tag("doeGuitar.jpg", class: "d-block w-100" )%>

          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block white-bg">
            <h5 class="carousel-overlay-title">The Musicians</h5>
            <p class="carousel-overlay-content">We help each other become stronger. Music is one of the purest ways to
              express one's feelings, and it's nice too.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= link_to image_tag("tahoe2019.jpg", class: "d-block w-100") %>

          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block white-bg">
            <h5 class="carousel-overlay-title">Studying in Tahoe</h5>
            <p class="carousel-overlay-content">A <strong>Tahoe</strong> trip would be far too ideal for a Berkley
              student, that's why we bring our books with us!</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= link_to image_tag("sathergate.jpg", class: "d-block w-100") %>

          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block white-bg">
            <h5 class="carousel-overlay-title">Blocking Sather Gate</h5>
            <p class="carousel-overlay-content">Once a year on the Remembrance Day of the Armenian Genocide, we block
              the Sather gate to raise awareness</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= link_to image_tag("doeCamp.jpg", class: "d-block w-100") %>

          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block white-bg">
            <h5 class="carousel-overlay-title">Talks in the Glade</h5>
            <p class="carousel-overlay-content">The strive for justice units us, but it also makes our identity. </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= link_to image_tag("armandattack.jpg", class: "d-block w-100") %>

          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block white-bg">
            <h5 class="carousel-overlay-title"><strong>The Armand</strong></h5>
            <p class="carousel-overlay-content">Watch where you step. The Big Brother is watching.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= link_to image_tag("tahoepic.jpg", class: "d-block w-100") %>

          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block white-bg">
            <h5 class="carousel-overlay-title">The Brothers Karamazov</h5>
            <p class="carousel-overlay-content">I can see the sun, but even if I cannot see the sun, I know that it
              exists. And to know that the sun is there - that is living (says the guy on the right).</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= link_to image_tag("arikconcert.jpg", class: "d-block w-100") %>

          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block white-bg">
            <h5 class="carousel-overlay-title">The Arik</h5>
            <p class="carousel-overlay-content">Arik is arguably the most skilled person ever part of the ASA. He is the
              Jack of all trades, master of all.
              Singing is only of these dozen perfected skills. Others include skinny-dipping and hitting the elevator
              button multiple times.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= link_to image_tag("dianaconcert.jpg", class: "d-block w-100") %>

          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block white-bg">
            <h5 class="carousel-overlay-title">The Voice of an Angel</h5>
            <p class="carousel-overlay-content">Few people can sing like Diana. She blesses everyone attending with her
              incredible performances.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= link_to image_tag("calday.jpg", class: "d-block w-100") %>

          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block white-bg">
            <h5 class="carousel-overlay-title">In front of the Doe</h5>
            <p class="carousel-overlay-content">We gather together to enjoy each other's companies, play games, and talk
              about life.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= link_to image_tag("food.jpg", class: "d-block w-100") %>

          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block white-bg">
            <h5 class="carousel-overlay-title">Delicious Baklava</h5>
            <p class="carousel-overlay-content">As a part of the annual cultural show, guests are introduced to the best
              of the Armenian culture, from food to dancing and from history to reality.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-bs-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
      </a>
      <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-bs-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="secondBody container-fluid">
    <h1 class="mission">Our Mission</h1>
    <p class="mission">The Armenian Students Association at the University of California, Berkeley was founded in 1976
      and its mission since then has been to provide a community where Armenian students at Cal can embrace their
      heritage and cultivate a spirit of appreciation towards Armenian history and culture through social, cultural,
      philanthropic, and professional events.

      ASA strives to foster and support its members as well as enhance their college experience at Cal by allowing them
      to come together and connect with their roots, give back to their community, and celebrate their culture and
      history without any outside political affiliations and/or religious influence. </p>
  </div>


  <hr class="sep-3">
  <div class="execBody container">
    <div class="execHeader">
      <h1>Meet our Exec</h1>
    </div>

    <% @execs.each_with_index do |exec, idx| %>
      <% if idx % 3 == 0%>
        <div class="execRow row">
      <% end %>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <% if exec.image.attached? %>
          <%= image_tag(url_for(exec.image), class: "exec-image") %>
        <% else %>
          <%= image_tag("profile-picture", class: "profile-picture")%>
        <% end %>
        <div class="execSubs">
          <h4 class="mainChairName"><%= exec.name %></h4>
          <h5 class="mainChairTitle"><%= exec.role %></h5>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% if (idx+1) % 3 == 0%>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>

  </div>
  
  <%= render 'layouts/footer' %>
</body>

